OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHIV drugs given to pigs and
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fchickens in Uganda         
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Uganda's National Drug Authority has   
OL,6, admitted it knew HIV medicine was being
OL,7, used to fatten up animals in 2014 but  
OL,8, did not warn the public.               
OL,10,FThe regulator's senior drugs inspector 
OL,11,FAmos Atumanya told parliament it became
OL,12,Faware anti-retrovirals were being given
OL,13,Fto pigs and chickens to treat them.    
OL,15,FMr Atumanya said that for humans,      
OL,16,Fconsuming small quantities of the drugs
OL,17,Fin food could be dangerous.            
OL,19,FBut the NDA has since tried to downplay
OL,20,Fhis comments.                          
